    N = int(input())

    l = set()

        if N > 0:
            r = plus(N)
            l.add(r)

def plus(N):
    p = 0
    n = 0
    while True:
        p += pow(2, n)
        if p >= N:
            break
        n += 2
    return n
def minus(N):
    p = 0
    n = 1
    while True:
        p -= pow(2, n)
        if p <= N:
            break
        n += 2
    return n
